dct_description_sm: Depths shown by isolines, soundings and gradient tints.
Includes hydrographic survey index and information, depth gradient diagram, and index to adjoining maps.
Also available via Internet from the NGDC NOAA web site. Address as of 12/21/06: http://www.ngdc.noaa.gov/mgg/bathymetry/maps/previews/F-99.pdf; current access via PURL.
